    <h2>Considering a wrongful death case review?</h2>
    <p>
      Learn more about how wrongful death lawsuits work and what factors may affect whether surviving family
      members may have a potential claim.
    </p>
    <div class="final__ctas">
      <a href="case-review.html" class="btn btn--dark btn--lg">Start Free Case Review</a>
